title: RHOSLC: And All That Jazz Tickets
description:
The Real Housewives of Salt Lake City trip to Scottsdale, AZ goes awry as Whitney voices rumors about Lisa sleeping with a man for Utah Jazz tickets. Sounds like a case for Nancy Drew!

Check this recap out on Crappens on Demand here: https://www.patreon.com/posts/73272577/
